# Signature Pieces – Furniture Mobile Application

## Project Overview

Designed a mobile application for furniture shopping using Human-Computer Interaction (HCI) principles and user-centered design concepts.

## Key Activities

- Designed user interfaces and application screens.
- Applied usability and accessibility principles.
- Created a user-centered shopping experience.
- Evaluated and improved the user journey.

## Skills

HCI, UX Design, UI Design, User-Centered Design, Usability Testing, Accessibility
